the moral of the story is...

00:02:21.392 --> 00:02:23.334
the moral of the story
is that there is no moral.

00:02:23.434 --> 00:02:24.936
There is no morality.

00:02:25.036 --> 00:02:26.418
I mean. what is
the morality of this?

00:02:26.518 --> 00:02:28.500
I wouldn't be able
