influence on Jamal's thinking.

00:44:40.530 --> 00:44:42.913
Suddenly he saw
that freedom of expression

00:44:43.013 --> 00:44:45.556
was the key to reform
in the Arab world

00:44:45.656 --> 00:44:47.959
and especially
in Saudi Arabia.

00:44:48.059 --> 00:44:49.520
[hammers banging]

