Prince Al-Waleed bin Talal.

00:45:10.924 --> 00:45:13.868
And at first. it seemed
like there might be room

00:45:13.968 --> 00:45:16.991
for an independent voice
in the kingdom.

00:45:17.091 --> 00:45:19.974
speaking Arabic

