a very good relationship

00:45:37.033 --> 00:45:38.695
with Prince Waleed.

00:45:38.795 --> 00:45:42.179
You know. the infamous
investor. Mr. Citibank.

00:45:42.279 --> 00:45:43.861
that made a lot of money.

00:45:43.961 --> 00:45:46.464
So. you know. he's a very
well-known individual

00:45:46.564 --> 00:45:48.065
on the international scene

00:45:48.165 --> 00:45:50.548
and has always been
an outspoken member

00:45:50.648 --> 00:45:52.510
of the Saudi royal family.

00:45:52.610 --> 00:45:54.553
but at the same time. again.
very much like Jamal.

00:45:54.653 --> 00:45:57.636
always very much
within the construct

00:45:57.736 --> 00:45:59.438
